OL,7,FAn increasing number of voices from
OL,8,Fwithin the industry, including former
OL,9,FBBC managers, have criticised the
OL,10,FBBC's local radio plans.  MPs from
OL,11,Fvarious constituencies have also
OL,12,Fwritten to the BBC director-general,
OL,13,FTim Davie, expressing their
OL,14,Fopposition to the cuts at local
OL,15,Fstations.
OL,17,FLast week, 93% of BBC journalists who
OL,18,Ftook part in a survey, expressed no
OL,19,Fconfidence in the BBC Local senior
OL,20,Fleadership team.
OL,3,CLocal BBC TV, radio and online
OL,4,Cservices in England hit by strike
OL,5,Caction
