OL,7,FSpeaking on BBC Look North yesterday,
OL,8,Fdirector of production, BBC Local,
OL,9,FJason Horton said: "We have to serve
OL,10,Fall of our audiences. And my job is
OL,11,Fto make sure that across your area,
OL,12,Facross Cornwall and Devon, across the
OL,13,FNorth East, across the South East, we
OL,14,Fare reaching as many people as we
OL,15,Fpossibly can, with all of our
OL,16,Fservices."
OL,18,FThe National Union of Journalists
OL,19,Fissued a statement on social media on
OL,20,F2nd June, explaining the background
OL,21,Fto the 48-hour strike:
