OL,7,F"In May 2022 the NUJ was told a
OL,8,F'digital review' was underway in BBC
OL,9,FLocal. We asked to be part of the
OL,10,Fproject team, to feed in ideas. A
OL,11,Ffull consultation, if you like.
OL,13,F"This didn't happen and we, like all
OL,14,Four colleagues, heard nothing until
OL,15,FOctober, when the Digital First
OL,16,Fstrategy was announced. A formal
OL,17,Fconsultation opened with the joint
OL,18,Funions, but there was no public
OL,19,Fconsultation, no published research,
OL,20,Fto accompany this.
OL,3,CLocal BBC TV, radio and online
OL,4,Cservices in England hit by strike
OL,5,Caction
