OL,7,F"Now our members have delivered
OL,8,Fanother decisive result, those
OL,9,Fleaders have a clear choice. Pause
OL,10,Fthis plan, have a proper public
OL,11,Fconsultation and work with us. The
OL,12,Fdoor remains open."
